    "registry_loader.py reads this; run_signals.py and regime/regime_rules.py derive STRATEGY_MAP and ALL_STRATEGIES from it.",
    "Fields per entry:",
    "  id          : integer, must be unique. Used as the strategy_id in gold.strategy_signals.",
    "  name        : short label shown in dashboards and logs.",
    "  class_path  : 'module.path:ClassName' — must be importable from the agents/etl/ workspace root.",
