    "  enabled     : true = run in daily cron and write signals. false = imported only, NEVER writes signals.",
    "  asset_class : {equity, crypto, fx, commodity}. Used for filtering and reporting.",
    "  params      : free-form dict the strategy class reads (basket, lookback windows, thresholds...).",
    "                Strategies that don't yet read from params still work — they ignore this field.",
